quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  8,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  8,1,"tum se infaal ke mutaliq puchhte hain? kaho “infaaltu Allah aur uss ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke hain, pas tum log Allah se daro aur apne aapas ke taluqaat durust karo aur Allah aur uss ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki itaat karo agar tum momin ho """
  8,2,sachey ahal imaan to woh log hain jin ke dil Allah ka zikar sun kar laraz jatay hain aur jab Allah ki ayaat un ke samnay parhi jati hain to un ka imaan barh jata hai aur woh apne rab par aetmaad rakhtay hain
  8,3,jo namaz qaim karte hain aur jo kuch hum ne un ko diya hai is mein se ( hamari raah mein ) kharch karte hain
  8,4,aisay hi log haqeeqi momin hain un ke liye un ke rab ke paas barray darjay hainKasoroo-n se dar guzar hai aur behtareen rizaq hai
  8,5,( iss maal ghanemat ke maamla mein bhi waisi hi soorat paish aa rahi hai jaisi uss waqt paish aayi thi jabkay ) tera rab tujhe haq ke sath tairay ghar se nikaal laya tha aur mominoun mein se aik giroh ko yeh sakht nagawaar tha
  8,6,woh is haq ke maamla mein tujh se jhagar rahay thay Daran halay ke woh saaf saaf numaya ho chuka tha un ka haal yeh tha ke goya woh aankhon dekhe mout ki taraf hankay ja rahay hain
  8,7,yaad karo woh mauqa jab ke Allah tum se wada kar raha tha ke dono garohoon mein se aik tumhe mil jaye ga tum chahtay thay ke kamzor giroh tumhe miley magar Allah ka iradah yeh tha ke apne arshadat se haq ko haq kar dukhaay aur kafiroon ki jarr kaat day
  8,8,taakay haq haq ho kar rahay aur baatil baatil ho jaye khuwa mujrimon ko yeh kitna hi nagawaar ho
  8,9,aur woh mauqa yaad karo jabkay tum apne rab se faryaad kar rahay thay jawab mein is ne farmaya ke mein tumhari madad ke liye pay Dur pay aik hazaar farishtay bhaij raha hon
  8,10,"yeh baat Allah ne tumhe sirf is liye bta di ke tumhe khushkhabri ho aur tumahray dil is se mutmaen ho jayen, warna madad to jab bhi hoti hai Allah hi ki taraf se hoti hai, yaqeenan Allah zabardast aur Dana hai"
  8,11,"aur woh waqt jabkay Allah apni taraf se ghunodghi ki shakal mein tum par itminan o be khofi ki kefiyat taari kar raha tha, aur aasman se tumahray oopar pani barsa raha tha taakay tumhe pak kere aur tum se shetan ki daali hui najasat door kere aur tumhari himmat banda-hay aur is ke zareya se tumahray qadam jama day"
  8,12,"aur woh waqt jabkay tumhara rab firshton ko ishara kar raha tha ke “min tumahray sath hon, tum ehley imaan ko saabit qadam rakho, mein abhi un kafiroon ke dilon mein Roab daaley deta hon, pas tum un ki gardnon par zarb aur joor joor par chout lagao """
  8,13,yeh is liye ke un logon ne Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ka muqaabla kya aur jo Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ka muqaabla kere Allah is ke liye nihayat sakht geer hai
  8,14,"yeh hai tum logon ki saza, ab is ka maza chako, aur tumhe maloom ho ke haq ka inkaar karne walon ke liye dozakh ka azaab hai"
  8,15,"ae imaan laane walo, jab tum aik lashkar ki soorat mein kufar se dochar ho to un ke muqaabla mein peeth nah phero"
  8,16,"jis ne aisay mauqa par peeth pheri, ila yeh ke jungi chaal ke tor par aisa kere ya kisi doosri fouj se ja milnay ke liye, to woh Allah ke ghazab mein ghar jaye ga, uss ka thikana jahannum hoga, aur woh bohat burii jaye baaz gasht hai"
  8,17,"pas haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum ne inhen qatal nahi kya balkay Allah ne un ko qatal kya aur to ne nahi phenka balkay Allah ne phenka ( aur mominoun ke haath jo iss kaam mein istemaal kiye gay ) to yeh is liye tha ke Allah mominoun ko aik behtareen azmaish se kamyabi ke sath guzaar day, yaqeenan Allah sُnne wala aur jan-nay wala hai"
  8,18,yeh maamla to tumahray sath hai aur kafiroon ke sath maamla yeh hai ke Allah un ki chalon ko kamzor karne wala hai
  8,19,"( inn kafiroon se keh do ) “agartum faisla chahtay thay to lau, faisla tumahray samnay aa gaya ab baz aa jao to tumahray hi liye behtar hai, warna phir palat kar isi hamaqat ka iada karo ge to hum bhi isi saza ka iada karen ge aur tumhari jamiat, khuwa woh kitni hi ziyada ho, tumahray kuch kaam nah aa sakay gi Allah mominoun ke sath hai """
  8,20,"ae imaan laane walo, Allah aur uss ke rasool ki itaat karo aur hukum sُnne ke baad is se sartabi nah karo"
  8,21,unn logon ki terhan nah ho jao jinhon ne kaha ke hum ne suna halaank woh nahi suntay
  8,22,yaqeenan khuda ke nazdeek bad tareen qisam ke janwar woh behray gungay log hain jo aqal se kaam nahi letay
  8,23,agar Allah ko maloom hota ke un mein kuch bhi bhalai hai to woh zaroor inhen sُnne ki tofeq deta ( lekin bhalai ke baghair ) agar woh un ko sunwata to woh be rukhi ke sath munh phair jatay
  8,24,"ae imaan laane walo, Allah aur is ke rasool ki pukaar par labaik kaho jabkay rasool tumhe is cheez ki taraf bhulay jo tumhe zindagi bakhsnay wali hai, aur jaan rakho ke Allah aadmi aur is ke dil ke darmain haail hai aur isi ki taraf tum samete jao ge"
  8,25,aur bachcho uss ftne se jis ki shamat makhsoos tor par sirf aُnhi logon taq mehdood nah rahay gi jinhon ne tum mein se gunah kya ho aur jaan rakho ke Allah sakht saza dainay wala hai
  8,26,"yaad karo woh waqt jabkay tum thoray thay, zameen mein tum ko be zor samgha jata tha, tum drtay rehtay thay ke kahin log tumhe mita nah den phir Allah ne tum ko jaye panah muhayya kar di, apni madad se tumahray haath Mazboot kiye aur tumhe acha rizaq pohanchaya, shayad ke tum shukar guzaar bano"
  8,27,"ae imaan laane walo, jantay bojhtay Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke sath khayanat nah karo, apni amanaton mein ghaddari ke murtakib nah ho"
  8,28,aur jaan rakho ke tumahray maal aur tumhari aulaad haqeeqat mein samanِ azmaish hain aur Allah ke paas ajar dainay ke liye bohat kuch hai
  8,29,"ae imaan laane walo, agar tum khuda tarsi ikhtiyar karo ge to Allah tumahray liye kasoti baham pouncha day ga aur tumhari buraiyon ko tum se door kar day ga, aur tumahray qasoor maaf kar day ga Allah bara fazl frmane wala hai"
  8,30,woh waqt bhi yaad karne ke qabil hai jabkay munkareen haq tairay khilaaf tadbeerye soch rahay thay ke tujhe qaid kar den ya qatal kar dalain ya jala watan kar den woh apni chaalein chal rahay thay aur Allah apni chaal chal raha tha aur Allah sab se behtar chaal chalne wala hai
  8,31,"jab un ko hamari ayaat sunai jati theen to kehte thay ke “haa-n sun liya hum ne, hum chahain to aisi hi baatein hum bhi bana satke hain, yeh to wohi porani kahaniyan hain jo pehlay se log kehte chalay aa rahay hain """
  8,32,"aur woh baat bhi yaad hai jo onhon ne kahi thi ke “khudaya agar yeh waqai haq hai aur teri taraf se hai to hum par aasman se pathar barsa day ya koi dard naak azaab hum par le aa """
  8,33,uss waqt to Allah un par azaab nazil karne wala nah tha jabkay to un ke darmain mojood tha aur nah Allah ka yeh qaida hai ke log astaghfar kar rahay hon aur woh un ko azaab deeday
  8,34,"lekin ab kyun nah woh un par azaab nazil kere jabkay woh masjid haraam ka rasta rok rahay hain, halaank woh is masjid ke jaaiz matwalli nahi hain is ke jaaiz matwalli to sirf ehley taqwa hi ho satke hain magar aksar log is baat ko nahi jantay"
  8,35,"beeet Allah ke paas un logon ki namaz kya hoti hai, bas seetiyan bjate aur taliyan pitte hain pas ab lau, iss azaab ka maza chako apne uss Inkaar haq ki Padaash mein jo tum karte rahay ho"
  8,36,"jin logon ne haq ko maan-ne se inkaar kya hai woh apne maal khuda ke rastay se roknay ke liye sirf kar rahay hain aur abhi aur kharch karte rahen ge magar aakhir-kaar yahi koshishen un ke liye pachtaway ka sabab banin gi, phir woh maghloob hon ge, phir yeh kafir jahannum ki taraf ghair laaye jayen ge"
  8,37,taakay Allah gandagi ko pakizgee se chhant kar allag kere aur har qisam ki gandagi ko mila kar akhatta kere phir is plnde ko jahannum mein jhonk day yahi log asli diwanayhain
  8,38,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un kafiroon se kaho ke agar ab bhi baz aa jayen to jo kuch pehlay ho chuka hai is se dar guzar kar liya jaye ga, lekin agar yeh isi pichli rawish ka iada karen ge to guzashta qomon ke sath jo kuch ho chuka hai woh sab ko maloom hai"
  8,39,"ae imaan laane walo, un kafiroon se jung karo yahan taq ke fitnah baqi nah rahay aur deen poora ka poora Allah ke liye ho jaye phir agar woh fitnah se rُk jayen to un ke aamaal ka dekhnay wala Allah hai"
  8,40,aur agar woh nah manen to jaan rakho ke Allah tumhara sarparast hai aur woh behtareen haami o madad gaar hai
  8,41,"aur tumhe maloom ho ke jo kuch maal ghanemat tum ne haasil kya hai is ka panchawan hissa Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam aur rishta daaron aur yatimon aur miskeeno aur musafiron ke liye hai agar tum imaan laaye ho Allah par aur is cheez par jo faislay ke roz, yani dono foujon ki mdbhirh ke din, hum ne apne bande par nazil ki thi, ( to yeh hissa bakhushi ada karo ) Allah har cheez par Qadir hai"
  8,42,"yaad karo woh waqt jabkay tum waadi ke iss janib thay aur woh doosri janib parao daaley hue thay aur qaafla tum se neechay ( saahil ) ki taraf tha agar kahin pehlay se tumahray aur un ke darmain muqaabla ki qarardad ho chuki hoti to tum zaroor is mauqa par pehlu tehi kar jatay, lekin jo kuch paish aaya woh is liye tha ke jis baat ka faisla Allah kar chuka tha usay zahoor mein le aeye taakay jisay halaak hona hai woh Daleel roshan ke sath halaak ho aur jisay zindah rehna hai woh Daleel roshan ke sath zindah rahay, yaqeenan khuda sُnne wala aur jan-nay wala hai"
  8,43,"aur yaad karo woh waqt jabkay ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, khuda unn ko tumahray khawab mein thora dikha raha tha, agar kahin woh tumhe unn ki tadaad ziyada dikha deta to zaroor tum log himmat haar jatay aur larai ke maamla mein jhagra shuru kar dete, lekin Allah hi ne iss se tumhe bachaaya, yaqeenan woh seenon ka haal taq jaanta hai"
  8,44,"aur yaad karo jab ke muqablay ke waqt khuda ne tum logon ki nigahon mein dushmanon ko thora dekhaya aur un ki nigahon mein tumhe kam kar ke paish kya, taakay jo baat honi thi ussay Allah zahoor mein le aeye, aur aakhir-kaar saaray mamlaat Allah hi ki taraf rujoo karte hain"
  8,45,"ae imaan laane walo, jab kisi giroh se tumhara muqaabla ho to saabit qadam raho aur Allah ko kasrat se yaad karo, tawaqqa hai ke tumhe kamyabi naseeb ho gi"
  8,46,"aur Allah aur is ke rasool ki itaat karo aur aapas mein jhagro nahi warna tumahray andar kamzoree peda ho jaye gi aur tumhari howa akhar jaye gi sabr se kaam lau, yaqeenan Allah sabr karne walon ke sath hai"
  8,47,aur unn logon ke se rang dhang nah ikhtiyar karo jo apne gharon se itratay aur logon ko apni shaan dikhata hue niklay aur jin ki rawish yeh hai ke Allah ke rastay se roktay hain jo kuch woh kar rahay hain woh Allah ki girift se bahar nahi hai
  8,48,"zara khayaal karo is waqt ka jab ke shetan ne un logon ke kartoot un ki nigahon mein khushnuma bana kar dukhaay thay aur un se kaha tha ke aaj koi tum par ghalib nahi aa sakta aur yeh ke mein tumahray sath hon magar jab dono garohoon ka aamna saamna howa to woh ultay paon phir gaya aur kehnay laga ke mera tumhara sath nahi hai, mein woh kuch dekh raha hon jo tum log nahi dekhte, mujhe khuda se dar lagta hai aur khuda barri sakht saza dainay wala hai"
  8,49,"jab ke munafiqeen aur woh sab log jin ke dilon ko rog laga howa hai, keh rahay thay ke un logon ko to inn ke deen ne khabt mein mubtala kar rakha hai halaank agar koi Allah par bharosa kere to yaqeenan Allah bara zabardast aur Dana hai"
  8,50,kash tum uss haalat ko dekh satke jabkay farishtay maqtool kafiroon ki roohein qabz kar rahay thay woh un ke cheharon aur un ke kolhon par zrbin lagatay jatay thay aur kehte jatay thay “Loab julne ki saza bhugto
  8,51,"yeh woh jaza hai jis ka samaan tumahray apne hathon ne paishgi muhayya kar rakha tha, warna Allah to apne bundon par zulm karne wala nahi hai """
  8,52,yeh maamla un ke sath usi terhan paish aaya jis terhan aalِ firaon aur un se pehlay ke doosray logon ke sath paish aata raha hai ke unhon ne Allah ki ayaat ko maan-ne se inkaar kya aur Allah ne un ke gunaaho par inhen pakar liya Allah qowat rakhta hai aur sakht saza dainay wala hai
  8,53,yeh Allah ki iss sunnat ke mutabiq howa ke woh kisi Nemat ko jo is ne kisi qoum ko ataa ki ho is waqt taq nahi badalta jab taq ke woh qoum khud apne trzِ amal ko nahi badal deti Allah sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai
  8,54,aalِ firaon aur un se pehlay ki qomon ke sath jo kuch paish aaya woh isi zabita ke mutabiq tha unhon ne apne rab ki ayaat ko jhtlaya tab hum ne un ke gunaaho ki Padaash mein inhen halaak kya aur all firaon ko ghark kar diya yeh sab zalim log thay
  8,55,yaqeenan Allah ke nazdeek zameen par chalne wali makhlooq mein sab se badter woh log hain jinhon ne haq ko maan-ne se inkaar kar diya phir kisi terhan woh usay qubool karne par tayyar nahi
  8,56,( khasosan ) un mein se woh log jin ke sath to ne moahida kya phir woh har mauqa par is ko torte hain aur zara khuda ka khauf nahi karte
  8,57,pas agar yeh log tumhe larai mein mil jayen to un ki aisi khabar lau ke un ke baad jo doosray log aisi rawish ikhtiyar karne walay hon un ke hawaas bakhta ho jayen tawaqqa hai ke ke bad ohdon ke iss injaam se woh sabaq len ge
  8,58,"aur agar kabhi tumhe kisi qoum se khayanat ka andesha ho to is ke muahiday ko alania is ke agay pheink do, yaqeenan Allah خائنوں ko pasand nahi karta"
  8,59,"munkareen haq is ghalat fehmi mein nah rahen ke woh baazi le gay, yaqeenan woh hum ko hara nahi satke"
  8,60,"aur tum log, jahan taq tumhara bas chalay, ziyada se ziyada taaqat aur tayyar bandhay rehne walay ghoray unn ke muqaabla ke liye muhayya rakho taakay is ke zareya se Allah ke aur apne dushmanon ko aur un doosray ا'ada-a (dushmanoo) ko khauf zada karo jinhein tum nahi jantay magar Allah jaanta hai Allah ki raah mein jo kuch tum kharch karo ge is ka poora poora badal tumhari taraf paltayjaye ga aur tumahray sath hargiz zulm nah hoga"
  8,61,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, agar dushman sulah o salamti ki taraf mael hon to tum bhi is ke liye amaada ho jao aur Allah par bharosa karo, yaqeenan wohi suneney aur jan-nay wala hai"
  8,62,aur agar woh dhokay ki niyat rakhtay hon to tumahray liye Allah kaafi hai wohi to hai jis ne apni madad se aur mominoun ke zareya se tumhari taied ki
  8,63,"aur mominoun ke dil aik doosray ke sath joor diye tum roye zameen ki saari doulat bhi kharch kar daaltay to inn logon ke dil nah joor satke thay magar woh Allah hai jis ne un logon ke dil jore, yaqeenan woh bara zabardast aur Dana hai"
  8,64,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tumahray liye aur tumahray pairo ehley imaan ke liye to bas Allah kaafi hai"
  8,65,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, mominoun ko jung par ubharo agar tum mein se bees aadmi sabir hon to woh do so par ghalib ayen ge aur agar so aadmi aisay hon to munkareen haq mein se hazaar admion par bhaari rahen ge kyunkay woh aisay log hain jo samajh nahi rakhtay"
  8,66,"acha, ab Allah ne tumhara boojh halka kya aur usay maloom howa ke abhi tum mein kamzoree hai, pas agar tum mein se so aadmi sabir hon to woh do so par aur hazaar aadmi aisay hon to do hazaar par Allah ke hukum se ghalib ayen ge, aur Allah un logon ke sath hai jo sabr karne walay hain"
  8,67,"kisi nabi ke liye yeh zaiba nahi hai ke is ke paas qaidi hon jab taq ke woh zameen mein dushmanon ko achi terhan kuchal nah day tum log duniya ke faiday chahtay ho, halaank Allah ke pishِ nazar akhirat hai, aur Allah ghalib aur hakeem hai"
  8,68,agar Allah ka noshta pehlay nah likha ja chuka hota to jo kuch tum logon ne liya hai is ki Padaash mein tum ko barri saza di jati
  8,69,pas jo kuch tum ne maal haasil kya hai usay khao ke woh halal aur pak hai aur Allah se drtay raho yaqeenan Allah dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai
  8,70,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum logon ke qabza mein jo qaidi hain un se kaho agar Allah ko maloom howa ke tumahray dilon mein kuch kher hai to woh tumhe uss se barh charh kar day ga jo tum se liya gaya hai aur tumhari khataien maaf kere ga, Allah dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  8,71,"lekin agar woh tairay sath khayanat ka iradah rakhtay hain to is se pehlay woh Allah ke sath khayanat kar chuke hain, chunancha isi ki saza Allah ne inhen di ke woh tairay qaboo mein aa gay, Allah sab kuch jaanta aur hakeem hai"
  8,72,"jin logon ne imaan qubool kya aur hijrat ki aur Allah ki raah mein apni jaanen larrain aur apne maal khupa-ay, aur jin logon ne hijrat karne walon ko jagah di aur un ki madad ki, wohi darasal aik dosray ke walii hain rahay woh log jo imaan to le aeye magar hijrat kar ke ( dar-us-slamm mein ) aa nahi gay to un se tumhara Wilayat ka koi talluq nahi hai jab taq ke woh hijrat kar ke nah aa jayen haan agar woh deen ke maamla mein tum se madad mangeen to un ki madad karna tum par farz hai, lekin kisi aisi qoum ke khilaaf nahi jis se tumhara moahida ho jo kuch tum karte ho Allah usay daikhta hai"
  8,73,jo log munkar haq hain woh aik dosray ki himayat karte hain agar tum yeh nah karo ge to zameen mein fitnah aur bara fasaad barpaa ho ga
  8,74,jo log imaan laaye aur jinhon ne Allah ki raah mein ghar baar chhorey aur jad-o-jehad ki aur jinhon ne panah di aur madad ki wohi sachey momin hain un ke liye khataon se dar guzar hai aur behtareen rizaq hai
  8,75,"aur jo log baad mein imaan laaye aur hijrat kar ke aa gay aur tumahray sath mil kar jad-o-jehad karne lagey woh bhi tum hi mein shaamil hain magar Allah ki kitaab mein khoon ke rishta daar aik dosray ke ziyada haqdaar hain, yaqeenan Allah har cheez ko jaanta hai"
